          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Measurements of  the  cross sections of B-10(g,p) and",
                " B-10(g,pn) with tagged photons have  been  performed",
                " at Eg = 66 - 103 MeV. The comparison of experimental",
                " cross section of B-10(g,p) reaction  and  the  cross",
                " section  deduced  by  scaling  of experimental cross",
                " section of B-10(g,pn) reaction is used for study how",
                " much  of  the  high  missing  energy B-10(g,p) cross",
                " section arises from the  (g,pn)  process  where  the",
                " photoneutron is not detected."
              ]
            }
          ],
